description.en:
SafeDog Protocol is a project inspired by SafeMoon protocol that aims to provide solutions to existing dilemma SafeMoon is facing right now. 100% community-driven project to contribute to decentralization. Contract ownership is renounced. We at SafeDog Protocol decentralization as the future of our finances. 

SafeDog Protocol aims to build a decentralized exchange where liquidity pool providers has option to lock the LP within the platform itself.
